df = pd.read_csv('/workspace/april-attendance-data.csv')

with pd.ExcelWriter('/workspace/macro-enabled-attendance.xlsm', engine='openpyxl') as writer:
    df.to_excel(writer, index=False, sheet_name='Attendance')

# VBA macro code
vba_code = '''
Private Sub Workbook_Open()
    Dim ws As Worksheet
    Set ws = ThisWorkbook.Sheets("Attendance")
    Dim lastRow As Long
    lastRow = ws.Cells(ws.Rows.Count, "A").End(xlUp).Row
    
    For i = 2 To lastRow
        If IsDate(ws.Cells(i, 1)) Then
            clockIn = TimeValue(ws.Cells(i, 1).Value)
            If clockIn > TimeValue("09:20:00") Then
                ws.Cells(i, 2).Value = ws.Cells(i, 2).Value - TimeSerial(2, 0, 0)
            End If
        End If
    Next i
End Sub
'''
